1593
02:44:18,795 --> 02:44:23,697
[SPEAKER_12]: So just, you know, asking for a review of like what the upcoming projects are I think is really great.

1594
02:44:23,717 --> 02:44:32,941
[SPEAKER_12]: And I think it's very reasonable to just request a review of how and when project information is posted to the website and communicated to residents.

1595
02:44:32,961 --> 02:44:34,961
[SPEAKER_12]: So very reasonable.

1596
02:44:35,702 --> 02:44:40,183
[SPEAKER_12]: I like the idea of having something in the city council rather than at a committee.

1597
02:44:40,523 --> 02:44:42,164
[SPEAKER_12]: So I think this is a great idea.

1598
02:44:42,244 --> 02:44:42,704
[SPEAKER_12]: Thank you so much.

1599
02:44:45,452 --> 02:44:49,795
[SPEAKER_25]: On the motion to approve by Councilor Scarpelli, seconded by Councilor Callahan.

