[SPEAKER_25]: Opposed?

1608
02:45:03,904 --> 02:45:04,424
[SPEAKER_25]: Motion passes.

1609
02:45:04,464 --> 02:45:05,085
[SPEAKER_25]: Councilor Scarpelli.

1610
