[SPEAKER_15]: Thank you.

1611
02:45:05,695 --> 02:45:12,738
[SPEAKER_15]: I think, again, with this, it's a resolution that requests that all utility projects will public notice, including information, season, construction, moratorium.

1612
02:45:13,178 --> 02:45:27,444
[SPEAKER_15]: I think that, to be a little of the fact, that one of the biggest things, the concerns that we had were that our neighbors actually thought that more than one, but a handful, thought that, especially the Riverside Ave project, was happening today.

1613
02:45:28,104 --> 02:45:33,907
[SPEAKER_15]: And with the situations that we're, with the weather and everything, we're really making

1614
